{"tid":2260540,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"錢國偉黃金歲月捧紅味之天使 扮PSY神似被正版激讚","createTime":"2020-10-27T15:38:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T15:02:52.000Z","uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"86f29b934763372947dc668970a3a4e183f6f214","tid":2260540,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T15:38:54.000Z","msg":"錢國偉曾經監製多個TVB節目，其中《獎門人》及《美女廚房》被視為大台皇牌節目，大受歡迎。06年推出的《美女廚房》，以一班美少女做明星助廚，締造出不少美女廚神，更藉此彈出被外界認識，如孫慧雪、藍莓劉俐、春卷王寶葆等，掀起一遍美少女襲電視圈熱，令觀眾層面年輕化。之後繼續以美女作招徠的一系列節目如《味分高下》及《耳分高下》等，已為人母的JJ(賈曉晨)及網絡紅人Coffee，都是從錢國偉的節目捧出。"},{"pid":"03484cc3514b05ef345cc462bd9624e1fffc0f25","tid":2260540,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T15:39:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20201027/1536pix/1603793865_1feb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20201027%2F1536pix%2F1603793865_1feb.jpg&h=c33fd010&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n古巨基是首位歌手找錢國偉做個人演唱會的監製。"},{"pid":"d25112cb7b7b5ebce9b3f406347641f343d88d16","tid":2260540,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T15:39:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20201027/1536pix/1603793862_c220.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20201027%2F1536pix%2F1603793862_c220.jpg&h=2f514c9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n13年，錢國偉監製好友伊健、錢嘉樂、林曉峰、陳小春及謝天華的古惑仔《歲月友情演唱會》，重燃古惑仔熱潮。"},{"pid":"180764faebecb0eec531f4759adf7a760eab3334","tid":2260540,"uid":44730,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T15:39:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"teal\">港版PSY</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n12年，韓國大叔歌手PSY的《江南Style》，風靡全球，甚少參與幕前演出的錢國偉，在好友鄭伊健和古巨基幫手下，為他炮製了《HongKong Style》，為錢國偉圓了幕前夢。由於錢國偉的外型與PSY很相似，所以MV一出街便熱爆網絡，「港版PSY」令錢國偉的人氣推至高峰，其神似度連當事人PSY都對這位山寨版相當讚賞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20201027/1536pix/1603793124_1c98.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20201027%2F1536pix%2F1603793124_1c98.jpg&h=c7de07c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20201027/1536pix/1603793206_3568.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20201027%2F1536pix%2F1603793206_3568.jpg&h=644e9c49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20201027/1536pix/1603793215_6865.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20201027%2F1536pix%2F1603793215_6865.jpg&h=5b2723d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86d3ffc6116744703829a4cf1e676cde6c8e8c1a","tid":2260540,"uid":44730,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T15:39:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20201027/1536pix/1603793220_5a12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20201027%2F1536pix%2F1603793220_5a12.jpg&h=882e1a49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正版與翻版同台，齊齊出席新濠天地活動。"},{"pid":"f00b0c7ea459d899d14196b682ce88f9a3878650","tid":2260540,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T15:40:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20201027/1536pix/1603793226_3166.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20201027%2F1536pix%2F1603793226_3166.jpg&h=9941eaac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一班味之天使為錢國偉客串拍《Hong Kong Style》MV"},{"pid":"8725cce2914aee4f91ff1bd33dd3aec28ab837d0","tid":2260540,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T15:40:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"teal\">《美人魚》成電影路上的突破</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n11年，錢國偉開始執導電影作品，最為人所知的有《喜愛夜蒲》系列，將年青一代的夜蒲生活呈現銀幕上，食正新一代觀眾口味。16年，周星馳投資兼執導的電影《美人魚》，請來錢國偉出任執行導演，成為他執導電影路上的一個突破。"},{"pid":"d96acf07007a47dc72639b951fe6ffbc4bdc99ba","tid":2260540,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T15:40:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20201027/1536pix/1603794295_9cb5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20201027%2F1536pix%2F1603794295_9cb5.jpg&h=68355c92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n16年，周星馳投資兼執導的電影《美人魚》，請來錢國偉出任執行導演，成為他執導電影路上的一個突破。"},{"pid":"9f04ca16d51b30eed2d0991b743f2f80effb318f","tid":2260540,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T15:40:45.000Z","msg":"在圈中的人緣極好，除了監製TVB節目、執導拍電影，他亦為不少歌手如古巨基、G.E.M、側田、鄭伊健、Big Four等製作演唱會。13年，錢國偉監製好友伊健、錢嘉樂、林曉峰、陳小春及謝天華的古惑仔《歲月友情演唱會》，重燃古惑仔熱潮。15年開始，《一起兄弟 歲月友情全國巡迴演唱會》在內地做了19場巡迴演出，最後一場在馬來西亞雲頂舉行。"},{"pid":"e2a7bd21e09a4768264236dd82e900ce969201c4","tid":2260540,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T15:40:58.000Z","msg":"他監製的節目娛樂性豐富，想不到他婚宴，亦極具娛樂及新聞性。15年，錢國偉與陳宛蔚在洲際酒店舉行婚宴，當晚星光熠熠，勁過台慶，不過林盛斌Bob在婚宴尾聲因為飲大咗，醉醺醺行上台，爆粗辣著在台上獻唱的陳小春，搞到小春掟咪爆粗之餘，還想衝去打Bob。幸而雙方及時被賓客拉開，事後Bob指自己醉酒斷片，承認失控，並向對方致歉。"},{"pid":"82413180da88d37a4d0fa7779d48f529e18a16a5","tid":2260540,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T15:41:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"teal\">陳志雲事件嚐盡冷暖</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n10年，廉政公署展開「威遠行動」，拘捕了當時的電視廣播有限公司電視廣播業務總經理陳志雲、節目監製錢國偉等人，指他們涉及貪污。錢國偉事後接受訪問時表示，當時他的心情一直跌到谷底，是人生最低潮的時候。保釋期間，錢國偉被暫停工作，嘗盡了人情冷暖。最後，廉署雖停了錢國偉的檔案，但TVB卻沒有讓他復職，心灰意冷的他決定辭職轉戰影圈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20201027/1536pix/1603793106_a69a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20201027%2F1536pix%2F1603793106_a69a.jpg&h=2b060eea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當年陳志雲事件，令錢國偉嚐盡冷暖，令他決定離開TVB，轉去影圈做導演。"},{"pid":"f9c9132ba32bb1e94eb2b689dd8772eb8ac30cc2","tid":2260540,"uid":19725,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T16:01:03.000Z","msg":"佢除左似連登仔衰咸濕，仲有衰d咩？"},{"pid":"f4dfef75c69ec4acf185f1672da3f74407fc8f15","tid":2260540,"uid":35221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T16:17:59.000Z","msg":"cctvb 真係可以一句聲都唔出，真係架勢"},{"pid":"cab52b3cf288d43093b3cbb217ed0e4fdd6d277d","tid":2260540,"uid":71166,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T17:26:43.000Z","msg":"rip🙏錢導"},{"pid":"dcfc87a418f9fe7e6020ef46011fcd654a49cda6","tid":2260540,"uid":279326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f4dfef75c69ec4acf185f1672da3f74407fc8f15","tid":2260540,"uid":35221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T16:17:59.000Z","msg":"cctvb 真係可以一句聲都唔出，真係架勢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:11:44.000Z","msg":"冷血無情tvb"},{"pid":"16130a6326615b34f92a5303e37d443ee2ddc67d","tid":2260540,"uid":56377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T08:40:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15d79a8e584abf2e998d31a3ce8280c2d0d4e45e","tid":2260540,"uid":56377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T08:43:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6984a04778437066a72ce0bfa71ed04626aca098","tid":2260540,"uid":56377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T08:59:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80a6631a65a9e0c85c19a19210dfa9377134a01a","tid":2260540,"uid":56377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T09:01:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b117ca9814f6bc047f9ff82cc3380955a14d04e","tid":2260540,"uid":56377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T09:06:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9b5e9c4c420db36f5640721b1417de6e53a076a","tid":2260540,"uid":56377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T09:12:18.000Z","msg":"中"},{"pid":"d0d0271cbb528152ab592974395995b246ebd403","tid":2260540,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcfc87a418f9fe7e6020ef46011fcd654a49cda6","tid":2260540,"uid":279326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f4dfef75c69ec4acf185f1672da3f74407fc8f15","tid":2260540,"uid":35221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T16:17:59.000Z","msg":"cctvb 真係可以一句聲都唔出，真係架勢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:11:44.000Z","msg":"冷血無情tvb"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T11:21:24.000Z","msg":"正仆街嚟<br />\n<br />\nbtw 時事臺又炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69695ffc747b41b3f05dc9eed972c68349b5ce7e","tid":2260540,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T15:02:52.000Z","msg":"其實點解話佢藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}